details.sectionContent: A Guest lecture conducted by Managing Director of Maharashtra Metro Rail Corp. Ltd. (Chief project manager of Bullet Train Project High Speed Rail)

A seminar will be conducted by Mr. Pradeep Ahirkar Managing Director of Maharashtra Metro Rail Corp. Ltd. (Chief project manager of Bullet Train Project High Speed Rail). Seminar will be on Most Awaited Project Internationally Recognized Collab with Japan’s Shinkenzen
Shinkenzen – Produces fastest bullet trains on Earth
